For more information, visit the meeting website

   http://www.bioconductor.org/help/course-materials/2015/BiocAsia2015/

If you'd like an opportunity to present your work, be sure to submit an abstract by 31st July.

Registration is free and will be managed as part of GIW/InCoB2015

    https://perdana.apbionet.org/giw-incob-2015/

